sequenceDiagram
    participant CP
    participant GCtrl
    participant ClsCtrl
    participant Core
    participant SW as Software

    CP->>GCtrl: kernel packet / reg info
    GCtrl->>GCtrl: kernel -> logic cluster
    GCtrl->>ClsCtrl: cluster config + cluster index
    ClsCtrl->>ClsCtrl: logic cluster -> block
    ClsCtrl->>Core: block dispatch
    Core->>Core: warp/SIMT execution
    Core-->>ClsCtrl: block/core ack
    ClsCtrl-->>GCtrl: cluster ack / done
    GCtrl-->>CP: kernel done / interrupt
    GCtrl-->>SW: exception or status report
